# ECIS Design System Tokens & Styling Rules

## Color System (CSS Variables Required)
Always use CSS variables, never hardcode hex values:

```css
/* Primary Palette */
--bg: #0f1f33;           /* Dark navy background */
--surface: #162840;      /* Card/surface backgrounds */  
--surface-2: #1c3251;    /* Secondary surfaces */
--text: #eef3fb;         /* Primary text */
--text-muted: #b7c6da;   /* Secondary text */
--border: #2d4f7c;       /* Borders and dividers */

/* Action Colors */
--action: #0077ff;       /* Electric blue - primary interactive */
--action-hover: #0066dd; /* Hover state */
--focus: #4da3ff;        /* Focus rings */
--accent: #d4af37;       /* Gold - premium highlights only */

/* Status Colors */
--success: #22c55e;
--warning: #f59e0b; 
--danger: #ef4444;
```

## Typography System
- **Headings:** `--font-heading: Montserrat, Oswald, system-ui, sans-serif` (weights 600-800)
- **Body:** `--font-body: Inter, Source Sans Pro, system-ui, sans-serif` (weights 400-500)
- **Scale:** xs(0.75rem) → sm(0.875rem) → base(1rem) → lg(1.125rem) → xl(1.25rem) → 2xl(1.5rem) → 3xl(1.875rem) → 4xl(2.25rem) → 5xl(3rem)
- **Line Heights:** tight(1.2), snug(1.35), normal(1.6)

## Spacing & Layout
- **Grid:** 12-column, max-width 1440px
- **Gutters:** 24-32px between columns
- **Page Padding:** 24px mobile, 48px desktop
- **Spacing Scale:** Use only 4/8px multiples: 0, 4px, 8px, 12px, 16px, 20px, 24px, 32px, 40px, 48px, 64px, 80px, 96px
- **Border Radius:** sm(6px), md(10px), lg(14px), xl(18px), 2xl(24px)

## Shadow System
```css
--shadow-sm: 0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,.12);    /* Subtle elements */
--shadow-md: 0 6px 16px rgba(0,0,0,.2);    /* Cards, buttons */
--shadow-lg: 0 12px 28px rgba(0,0,0,.28);  /* Modals, overlays */
```

## Motion & Transitions
```css
--duration-fast: 150ms;   /* Micro-interactions */
--duration-base: 220ms;   /* Standard transitions */
--duration-slow: 320ms;   /* Complex animations */
--easing-standard: cubic-bezier(.2,.8,.2,1);
```

## Tailwind Integration Rules
When using Tailwind classes, prefer semantic color names:
- `bg-bg` instead of `bg-[#0f1f33]`
- `text-action` instead of `text-[#0077ff]`
- `border-border` instead of `border-[#2d4f7c]`

## Gold Usage Guidelines
⚠️ **CRITICAL:** Gold (#d4af37) is for premium highlights ONLY:
- ✅ Accent borders, badge outlines, icon strokes
- ✅ Premium service indicators, awards, certifications
- ❌ NEVER use for primary buttons or main CTAs
- ❌ Keep usage ≤10% per page

## Image Treatment
- **Overlay for text legibility:** `linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(15,31,51,.65), rgba(15,31,51,.85))`
- **Style preference:** Real ECIS imagery (team, vehicles, command center)
- **Timing:** "Blue hour" photography preferred
- **Icons:** Geometric/line style (Lucide, Heroicons)

## Responsive Breakpoints
- **sm:** 640px (mobile landscape)
- **md:** 768px (tablet portrait) 
- **lg:** 1024px (tablet landscape/small desktop)
- **xl:** 1280px (desktop)
- **2xl:** 1536px (large desktop)

## Dark Mode Support
Respect `prefers-color-scheme: dark` with darker variants:
```css
@media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
  :root {
    --bg: #0b1726;
    --surface: #111f32;
    --surface-2: #16233a;
    --action: #4da3ff;
    --action-hover: #3a8be0;
    --focus: #6bb6ff;
  }
}
```